Individual: JDBC Program
Instructions:
Write a Java program (non-GUI preferred) to demonstrate the use of
JDBC.
The program should allow a user to do the following:
• Write a list of animal and its characteristics to a database using
JDBC
• Display the characteristics of an animal when that animal is selected.
Include a brief documentation (in the code or in a separate document)
to explain the input (if any), processing and output of the program.
Submit your assignment using the Assignment Files tab above.